snippet.title: Farm Together 2 - Steam Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The successful farming experience is back!

Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2418520/

Farm Together 2 improves over the original game in every way, offering a better polished experience and becoming the best way to enjoy your own farm!

Join the Discord Server: https://discord.gg/gZweKWPE
Join the Subreddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/FarmTogether/
